    "headline": "Amazon’s $8.3 billion Prime Day sends Wall Street a warning",
    "summary": "Amazon’s Prime Day is off to a solid start, but the main news may not be how much shoppers are shelling out. It may be what they’re buying. U.S. online spending on the first day of Amazon’s four-day Prime Day event jumped 5.3% to $8.3 billion across merchants from a year ago, Adobe Analytics said. ...",
